## Import


An existing resource can be imported using its type token, name, and identifier, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import azure-native:solutions:Appliance myAppliance /subscriptions/subid/resourceGroups/rg/providers/Microsoft.Solutions/appliances/myAppliance 
```
